<item>
            <title>[LU-11440] Make e2fsprogs-1.44.3-wc1 release</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11440</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Need to make a release of e2fsprogs-1.44.3-wc1 from the master-lustre-test branch. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This also needs a patch to &lt;tt&gt;lustre/Changelog&lt;/tt&gt; to update the release version. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
