                            <comment id="238205" author="gerrit" created="Sat, 8 Dec 2018 05:33:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oleg Drokin (green@whamcloud.com) merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/33766/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/33766/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11440&quot; title=&quot;Make e2fsprogs-1.44.3-wc1 release&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11440&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11440&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; misc: require ldiskfsprogs-1.44.3.wc1 or later&lt;br/&gt;
