                            <comment id="237873" author="utopiabound" created="Mon, 3 Dec 2018 22:26:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ubuntu changes should be in one or more of the&#160; &lt;tt&gt;debian/control*&lt;/tt&gt; files I believe.&#160; There doesn&apos;t seem to be an existing explicit dependency on e2fsprogs&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="237797" author="gerrit" created="Sat, 1 Dec 2018 18:10:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Andreas Dilger (adilger@whamcloud.com) uploaded a new patch: &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/33766&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/33766&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11440&quot; title=&quot;Make e2fsprogs-1.44.3-wc1 release&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11440&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11440&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; misc: require ldiskfsprogs-1.44.3.wc1 or later&lt;br/&gt;
